{"tid":2478567,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"亞視及董事局主席鄧俊杰被指開空頭支票 財務公司入稟追債","createTime":"2021-04-07T07:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T07:35:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"99383e08115b61cc74eb63d6f50d253a7b2dafa9","tid":2478567,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"上月初亞洲電視門外出現七人車上門追債事件，聯席主席鄧俊杰捲入錢債糾紛成為主角，事件驚動警方。涉事的謝氏財務事後入稟高等法院，向鄧俊杰及亞視控股追討8張空頭支票的欠款，涉及金額2,650萬元。<br />\n<br />\n原告分別為謝氏財務有限公司及謝兆凱，被告則為鄧俊杰和亞洲電視控股有限公司。入稟狀透露，涉及鄧俊杰的7張期票編號全部連貫，每張金額為350萬元，到期日分別由去年8月底至今年2月底，總數2,450萬元。謝兆凱將支票交到銀行後，全部被「打回頭」，原因是「戶口取消」。<br />\n<br />\n亞洲電視控股涉及的一張支票則涉款200萬元，謝氏財務指存入支票後亦遭「彈票」。謝氏財務已將事件通知兩名被告。兩原告現向兩被告追討支票欠款及相關利息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/G73C5IYKBJG3JAWSGDXIC6DXVA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FG73C5IYKBJG3JAWSGDXIC6DXVA%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtKGgm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=200f0f88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FG73C5IYKBJG3JAWSGDXIC6DXVA%2F&h=79a080f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/G73C5IYKBJG3JAWSGDXIC6DXVA/</a>"},{"pid":"8b1d03b5afdad9bf3f76547ec1d292981d734271","tid":2478567,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZcBcbTHDfLCavAMpc9fPwDCecx4DAtU42Gqw2gUa2Kzu?filename=A04kFDd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA04kFDd.jpg&h=aed0d8da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a44dd46d1a0c377ed9e4197647c7d381a0a4200b","tid":2478567,"uid":55955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:06:29.000Z","msg":"希望香港抗爭者有亞視咁強嘅生命力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec301f67d0a4a9d20fe1ee51bc2281203057808","tid":2478567,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":